        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "風鈴が揺れるたびに、コロコロと涼しげな音を立てる。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "小鳥がコロコロと可愛らしい声でさえずっている。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "昔の電話のダイヤルを回すと、コロコロと音を立てたのを覚えている。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 3,
        "gloss": "(changing) frequently (of opinions, conversation topic, etc.)",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "彼は意見がコロコロ変わるので、信用できない。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "あの店のメニューは、季節ごとにコロコロと入れ替わる。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "彼女は話の話題をコロコロと変えるので、ついていくのが大変だ。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 4,
        "gloss": "(losing) all too easily",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "今日のサッカーの試合は、まさかこんなにコロコロと点が入るとは思わなかった。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "彼女は相手の挑発に乗り、試合でコロコロと負けてしまった。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "あんな強いチーム相手に、ここまでコロコロと負けるとはね。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 5,
        "gloss": "chubby (and cute)",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "コロコロした赤ちゃんのほっぺは、触るととても気持ちいい。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "その犬は、コロコロと太った体型でとても愛らしい。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "彼の描くキャラクターは、どれもコロコロとした丸いフォルムが特徴だ。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 6,
        "gloss": "chirping (of insects)",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "秋の夜長に、虫たちがコロコロと鳴いている。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "草むらから、鈴虫がコロコロと澄んだ音色で鳴き声が聞こえる。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "コロコロと鳴くセミの声を聞くと、夏が来たなと感じる。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 7,
        "gloss": "croaking (of a frog)",
        "register": "standard",
